      "fn_code": "void\nuser_reg_add_builtin (const char *name, user_reg_read_ftype *read,\n\t\t      const void *baton)\n{\n  append_user_reg (&builtin_user_regs, name, read, baton,\n\t\t   XNEW (struct user_reg));\n}",
